h5355","last_touched":1660184086,"title":"联通没有开通 5G 套餐不能访问 5G 网络？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/872070","created":1660180652,"deleted":0,"content":"坐标广东佛山，运营商是中国联通，手机是红米 K30 5G 。\r\n\r\n没有开通 5G 套餐。以前试过，手机网络设置了 NR ，就能使用 5G 。为了省点电，手机网络设置了 LTE/WCDMA ，即没有开启 5G 。\r\n\r\n最近发现手机网络即使开启了 5G ，也不能访问。如果设置只使用 NR 的话，手机网络的图标显示小叉叉。其实也没什么，毕竟没有开 5G 套餐。但是前几天经过隔壁的江门市，可以使用 5G 网络。\r\n\r\n3G 升 4G 那时，联通是自动开启 4G ，不知道这次 5G 为什么这么搞。","content_rendered":"<p>坐标广东佛山，运营商是中国联通，手机是红米 K30 5G 。</p>\n<p>没有开通 5G 套餐。以前试过，手机网络设置了 NR ，就能使用 5G 。为了省点电，手机网络设置了 LTE/WCDMA ，即没有开启 5G 。</p>\n<p>最近发现手机网络即使开启了 5G ，也不能访问。如果设置只使用 NR 的话，手机网络的图标显示小叉叉。其实也没什么，毕竟没有开 5G 套餐。但是前几天经过隔壁的江门市，可以使用 5G 网络。</p>\n<p>3G 升 4G 那时，联通是自动开启 4G ，不知道这次 5G 为什么这么搞。</p>\n","last_modified":1660180652,"replies":13,"id":872070},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2827,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","stars":915,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":111002,"username":"Awes0me","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Awes0me","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9ad2/67ac/111002_mini.png?m=1658888975","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9ad2/67ac/111002_normal.png?m=1658888975","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9ad2/67ac/111002_large.png?m=1658888975","created":1429013905,"last_modified":1658888975},"last_reply_by":"aflynoob","last_touched":1660187990,"title":"PC 和 laptop 用户什么时候才能不为 surface 买单","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/872078","created":1660182033,"deleted":0,"content":"打算从 Chrome 切换到 edge ，试用了感觉这个浏览器完全就是为 surface 这些小屏触摸设备设计的，右上角的扩展图标间隔宽的离谱，右键菜单之间的间隔也是比 Chrome 宽很多，最离谱的是书签栏点开文件夹，半个屏幕都占满了，Chrome 一屏能显示完的，edge 要翻两页。\r\n\r\n而且这些问题在 win11 上也有体现，ui 的信息密度很低，完全不考虑键鼠用户。","content_rendered":"<p>打算从 Chrome 切换到 edge ，试用了感觉这个浏览器完全就是为 surface 这些小屏触摸设备设计的，右上角的扩展图标间隔宽的离谱，右键菜单之间的间隔也是比 Chrome 宽很多，最离谱的是书签栏点开文件夹，半个屏幕都占满了，Chrome 一屏能显示完的，edge 要翻两页。</p>\n<p>而且这些问题在 win11 上也有体现，ui 的信息密度很低，完全不考虑键鼠用户。</p>\n","last_modified":1660182064,"replies":12,"id":872078},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":188520,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3531,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":253305,"username":"xia0sheng","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xia0sheng","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2fa4/1991/253305_mini.png?m=1505306699","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2fa4/1991/253305_normal.png?m=1505306699","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2fa4/1991/253305_large.png?m=1505306699","created":1504885476,"last_modified":1505306699},"last_reply_by":"xia0sheng","last_touched":1660195398,"title":"如何看待腾讯会议电话入会功能限免自 2022 年 8 月 10 日起恢复为付费功能？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/872118","created":1660187254,"deleted":0,"content":"个人版还不能购买语音包，企业版是 1000 分钟 400 元\r\n\r\n\r\n![购买费用]( https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0282528dfee46931cc5bd0beaaa5b2bb_b.png \"购买费用\")","content_rendered":"<p>个人版还不能购买语音包，企业版是 1000 分钟 400 元</p>\n<p><img alt=\"购买费用\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0282528dfee46931cc5bd0beaaa5b2bb_b.png\" title=\"购买费用\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1660187254,"replies":11,"i